        "text": "Aug-Oct 1946 Sweden. Hundreds of rocket-like fiery objects were\nobserved.\nNov. 12 1946 Venus Inferior Conjunction\nNov. 12 1946 Providence Bay, Siberia. Huge fiery-white object\ncrossed over. NY Times"
